# Zepto vs Blinkit Analysis Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📊 Project Overview
This project presents a comparative analysis of Zepto and Blinkit using Power BI. 
It focuses on key metrics like delivery time, ratings, product demand, and payment preferences.

## 🎯 Objectives
- Compare performance of Zepto and Blinkit
- Analyze customer behavior and product demand
- Identify top-selling products and cities
- Evaluate delivery efficiency and ratings

## 📌 Key Insights
- Milk and Eggs are the most ordered products
- Mumbai has the highest order volume
- UPI is the most preferred payment method
- Average delivery time is around 15 minutes
- Ratings are close to 3, indicating scope for improvement

## 📈 Dashboard Features
- KPI Cards (Orders, Delivery Time, Ratings)
- Monthly order trends
- Product-wise demand analysis
- City-wise performance
- Payment mode distribution
- Interactive slicers (Quarter, Category, Brand)

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Power BI
- Data Cleaning & Visualization

